



## Editing Softwares

**Reignited uses transparency for a lot of purposes** and one easy example is Spyro's eye material. Transparency of the eye texture is used for adding an eye glint. It is recommended to have a software that can edit transparency.

Paint.net: https://www.getpaint.net/download.html    
GIMP: https://www.gimp.org/downloads/    
Krita: https://krita.org/en/download/krita-desktop/